resources.description: The sensitivity of accelerometer can be changed with the amplitude of carrier wave. Based on the modeling of accelerometer, the mechanical characteristics are analyzed and the relationship between the elastic force and electrostatic force is obtained. The stable region of accelerometer reduces while the amplitude of carrier wave increases.
resources.name: The Effect of Carrier Wave Voltage on Accelerometer Sensitivity
